Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • Item

  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    An object of this class represents an item within the marketplace.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Item()
      Constructs a new Item whose name, description, price, and category are empty-string, whose item id and seller id are -1, and whose quantity is 0.
      Item(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String description, java.lang.String price, int itemID, int sellerID, int quantity, java.lang.String category)
      Constructs a new Item that will have the given name, description, price, item id number, seller id number, quantity, and category.
